#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.25"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.25:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.25:0.2"
msgid "3. Uruvelavagga"
msgstr "3. At Uruvelā"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.25:0.3"
msgid "25. Brahmacariyasutta"
msgstr "25. The Spiritual Life"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.25:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Nayidaṃ, bhikkhave, brahmacariyaṃ vussati janakuhanatthaṃ, na "
"janalapanatthaṃ, na lābhasakkārasilokānisaṃsatthaṃ, na "
"itivādappamokkhānisaṃsatthaṃ, na ‘iti maṃ jano jānātū’ti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, this spiritual life is not lived for the sake of deceiving "
"people or flattering them, nor for the benefit of possessions, honor, or "
"popularity, nor for the benefit of winning debates, nor thinking, ‘So let "
"people know about me!’"

msgctxt "an4.25:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho idaṃ, bhikkhave, brahmacariyaṃ vussati saṃvaratthaṃ pahānatthaṃ "
"virāgatthaṃ nirodhatthanti."
msgstr ""
"This spiritual life is lived for the sake of restraint, giving up, fading "
"away, and cessation."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.25:2.1"
msgid "Saṃvaratthaṃ pahānatthaṃ,"
msgstr "The Buddha taught the spiritual life"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.25:2.2"
msgid "brahmacariyaṃ anītihaṃ;"
msgstr "not because of tradition,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.25:2.3"
msgid "Adesayi so bhagavā,"
msgstr "but for the sake of restraint and giving up,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.25:2.4"
msgid "nibbānogadhagāminaṃ;"
msgstr "and because it culminates in extinguishment."

# Note that the reading mahattebhi, which I use as does BB, is attested in the variant here, while BB used it even though he didn’t have it as a reading in his sources.
#. <br>
#. VAR: mahantehi → mahattebhi (mr)
msgctxt "an4.25:2.5"
msgid "Esa maggo mahantehi,"
msgstr "This is the path followed by the great souls,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.25:2.6"
msgid "anuyāto mahesibhi."
msgstr "the great hermits."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.25:3.1"
msgid "Ye ca taṃ paṭipajjanti,"
msgstr "Those who practice it"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.25:3.2"
msgid "yathā buddhena desitaṃ;"
msgstr "as the Buddha taught,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.25:3.3"
msgid "Dukkhassantaṃ karissanti,"
msgstr "following the teacher’s instructions,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.25:3.4"
msgid "satthusāsanakārino”ti."
msgstr "make an end of suffering.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.25:3.5"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
